title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-1.9 - Transfer of permit
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-1.9 - Transfer of permit

State Regulations
A permit may not be transferred to a vehicle that is
not registered with OGS. Transfer of permits may be made only in accordance
with section
296-1.4
of this

Subpart. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
296-1.9

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
